options.text: Give me a quest or else!
Just stop messing around and give me a quest!

b7dfb9f8-4cb5-4337-9a4c-a83cf978511b.title: <player>
b7dfb9f8-4cb5-4337-9a4c-a83cf978511b.text: Just stop messing around and give me a quest!

d570f5f4-cabf-4786-a863-a577981a11fc.title: Wizard Mizgog
d570f5f4-cabf-4786-a863-a577981a11fc.text: Ah now you're assuming I have one to give.

bba2912b-60be-41d6-8845-08587a49daa0.title: <player>
bba2912b-60be-41d6-8845-08587a49daa0.text: Give me a quest or else!

72bbcc05-b0bc-438b-918d-46236835e041.title: Wizard Mizgog
72bbcc05-b0bc-438b-918d-46236835e041.text: Or else what? You'll attack me?

03dd3960-da6b-4334-abee-7878447ba251.title: Wizard Mizgog
03dd3960-da6b-4334-abee-7878447ba251.text:
Well seeing as you asked nicely... I could do with some
help.

f3735032-3670-4f50-a49b-06f7d4eea458.title: Wizard Mizgog
f3735032-3670-4f50-a49b-06f7d4eea458.text:
The wizard Grayzag next door decided he didn't like
me so he enlisted an army of hundreds of imps.

48e1ec13-3032-413e-af18-d730c894fa48.title: Wizard Mizgog
48e1ec13-3032-413e-af18-d730c894fa48.text:
These imps stole all sorts of my things. Most of these
things I don't really care about, just eggs and balls of
string and things.

ca5d10fa-739d-468b-8fea-a5840c78968d.title: Wizard Mizgog
ca5d10fa-739d-468b-8fea-a5840c78968d.text:
But they stole my four magical beads. There was a red
one, a yellow one, a black one, and a white one.

5a12b45e-1d04-4f27-9457-83fd8446f771.title: Wizard Mizgog
5a12b45e-1d04-4f27-9457-83fd8446f771.text:
These imps have now spread out all over the kingdom.
Could you get my beads back for me?

options.text: I've better things to do than chase imps.

3c6938c4-98a4-4725-941b-cc5212119c8c.title: <player>
3c6938c4-98a4-4725-941b-cc5212119c8c.text: I've better things to do than chase imps.

c36872c4-ff63-45f6-ac25-344fc2141d4a.title: Wizard Mizgog
c36872c4-ff63-45f6-ac25-344fc2141d4a.text:
Well if you're not interested in the quests I have to
give you, don't waste my time by asking me for them.

db61f36c-4dfe-4293-8f2e-7607ed4c77fb.title: <player>
db61f36c-4dfe-4293-8f2e-7607ed4c77fb.text: I've not got them all yet.

55a279b2-49b1-4779-8f7b-e37287dc200d.title: Wizard Mizgog
55a279b2-49b1-4779-8f7b-e37287dc200d.text:
Well get on with it. I've lost a white bead, a red bead, a
black bead, and a yellow bead. Go kill some imps!

1129d864-af5e-4af8-88e6-d832d89b6cc4.title: Wizard Mizgog
1129d864-af5e-4af8-88e6-d832d89b6cc4.text: So how are you doing finding my beads?

e2e21546-1dcd-4163-9270-06672435702b.title: <player>
e2e21546-1dcd-4163-9270-06672435702b.text: I've got all four beads. It was hard work I can tell you.

3d7b760a-2d4b-484b-bf25-ee8f46213ca8.title: Wizard Mizgog
3d7b760a-2d4b-484b-bf25-ee8f46213ca8.text:
Give them here and I'll check that they really are MY
beads, before I give you your reward. You'll like it, it's
an amulet of accuracy.

7e5bed0b-1559-4f6f-b602-73d2efd51b7f.text: You hand over the beads for the wizard to check.

options.text: Do you know any interesting spells you could teach me?
Have you got another one of those fancy schmancy amulets?

9b56079e-2e6e-4f77-9295-ac741ffebce5.title: <player>
9b56079e-2e6e-4f77-9295-ac741ffebce5.text:
Have you got another one of those fancy schmancy
amulets?

8c48a628-2f3d-42f6-a144-4466824b02d4.title: Wizard Mizgog
8c48a628-2f3d-42f6-a144-4466824b02d4.text:
I have a few spare. I'd like one of each coloured bead
again in return, though! Black, white, yellow and red.

d33a2b92-471b-4d0f-b9c7-eb8f5da0de85.title: Note
d33a2b92-471b-4d0f-b9c7-eb8f5da0de85.text: Missing ability to trade for another amulet

4b96f435-49cf-4576-86bc-02fdb1c957f7.title: <player>
4b96f435-49cf-4576-86bc-02fdb1c957f7.text:
I don't have them all on me at the moment. I'll come
back when I have them!

4b6c40b9-bc5b-4f2a-8b6e-debdd830a3b7.title: <player>
4b6c40b9-bc5b-4f2a-8b6e-debdd830a3b7.text:
Do you know any interesting spells you could teach
me?"

f37092d3-e451-4dbf-9fe4-f51b5e68d631.title: Wizard Mizgog
f37092d3-e451-4dbf-9fe4-f51b5e68d631.text:
I don't think so, the type of magic I study involves
years of meditation and research.

6e472b7b-6d2f-4fa2-915e-f52736114b34.title: Wizard Mizgog
6e472b7b-6d2f-4fa2-915e-f52736114b34.text: No, everything is good with the world today.
